1
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:12,513
How much heart do you have to have

2
00:00:12,513 --> 00:00:15,155
to look past Krishna's Divinity?

3
00:00:18,079 --> 00:00:21,279
For that is not a factor in your relationship.

4
00:00:22,371 --> 00:00:25,837
We need to talk about our relationship!

5
00:00:31,143 --> 00:00:34,487
You can look past Krishna's Divinity.

6
00:00:34,487 --> 00:00:39,353
It is not a factor in your relationship.

7
00:00:39,353 --> 00:00:44,155
You just love Krishna the way He is.

8
00:00:44,964 --> 00:00:49,205
Reality is for Itself and by Itself.

9
00:00:49,810 --> 00:00:52,097
Like we think in this world who can do that?

10
00:00:52,097 --> 00:00:55,031
The mother.

11
00:00:55,814 --> 00:00:59,779
The son could become the president, prime minister...

12
00:00:59,779 --> 00:01:02,910
It is still her boy, her son.

13
00:01:02,910 --> 00:01:07,354
She is not seeing president, prime minister...

14
00:01:07,354 --> 00:01:09,677
She remembers so many things about him.

15
00:01:09,677 --> 00:01:12,686
She can actually suppress all of that.

16
00:01:12,686 --> 00:01:17,749
It cannot stand in the presence of her heartflow.

17
00:01:18,364 --> 00:01:20,842
If that can be true here,

18
00:01:20,842 --> 00:01:24,737
then think what is the position of Yashoda?

19
00:01:24,737 --> 00:01:26,235
We are told to preach

20
00:01:26,235 --> 00:01:28,580
Krishna is Supreme Personality of Godhead.

21
00:01:28,580 --> 00:01:30,704
Uhhhh!

22
00:01:30,704 --> 00:01:32,220
Do not say that!

23
00:01:32,220 --> 00:01:35,891
Those are vicious rumors where She lives.

24
00:01:35,891 --> 00:01:38,192
In this world we`re trying to make propaganda

25
00:01:38,192 --> 00:01:40,278
in favor of Krishna Conception.

26
00:01:40,278 --> 00:01:44,135
In That World that we aspire to serve,

27
00:01:44,135 --> 00:01:47,619
She is saying rumors of Krishna' s Divinity

28
00:01:47,619 --> 00:01:50,453
are that, the are rumors, the vicious rumors,

29
00:01:50,453 --> 00:01:52,899
started by envious people!

